RELEASE NOTES
=============

This is the release "1.4.0" of the doxphinx theme.
This is a "STABLE" release.

See https://docs.phyglos.org/doxphinx for more information.


MAJOR CHANGES
=============

* Added bottom border to subfooter area
* Allow customization of navigation item 0
* Tested with Sphinx 2.1.0

